# React / React Native

Source of truth: @ai/rules/common/react.md
React 18 addendum: @ai/rules/common/react-18.md

## Quick Rules

- Functional components only; no class components
- Hooks at top level; follow Rules of Hooks
- `useCallback` for handlers passed as props / deps of other hooks
- `useMemo` for expensive computations, not cheap ones
- `React.memo` for list-item components in FlatList
- No derived state via `useEffect` — compute in render
- Prefer `useDeferredValue` / `startTransition` for non-urgent updates
- No state updates inside render
- Cleanup in `useEffect` — cancel subscriptions, timers, abort controllers
